一般講嘅drug tolerance 都係指drug of dependence<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29916f8ffbbd26cee4ca07be1aaba65d365f97bd","tid":2454664,"uid":286206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8ddc344c30f577aaa3f809462d2699e2ced092d","tid":2454664,"uid":367224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T11:42:03.000Z","msg":"假設經濟負擔得起<br />\n如果快樂 健康 成績全部可以靠食藥得到又唔犯法 但會極度依賴同上癮 你會唔會食？<br />\n<br />\n其實經濟負擔個假設都未必需要<br />\n唔使買樓溝女都可以得到快樂 慳錢慳時間<br />\n唔使做運動 生活唔使考慮健康 又慳返啲精神<br />\n成績好(學業同事業)又揾得多<br />\n成世人就係返工揾錢 -&gt; 買藥 -&gt; 食藥 -&gt; loop<br />\n覺得唔開心或者人生冇意義又食藥開心返 唔會有機會俾你existential crisis <br />\n有冇人想過咁嘅人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T12:41:12.000Z","msg":"會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇政府精神科話失眠同緊張 3個月覆診一次開足90日鎮定劑同安眠藥比你 怕你唔上隱咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />合法吸毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"889f2848ea851430138f295d6449623de7f4338a","tid":2454664,"uid":127815,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b255db25e35caeb376e2b64129a9a82a901355e6","tid":2454664,"uid":97887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adfdced432c6dc49dccf6bdc0b3e839f42b193aa","tid":2454664,"uid":127815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7390247beec4ad91f23d4e5a41c2e90127d3958","tid":2454664,"uid":97887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T12:00:58.000Z","msg":"同埋就算無副作用，由有藥效到無藥效之間的空隙帶黎的對比同失落會令人想死<br />\n<br />\n有d人食抗抑鬱藥都係咁，一無藥效跌返落去，個落差唔係個個受到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T12:05:34.000Z","msg":"exact7ly 我就係人版<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\